OL,6,FCryptosporidium is a waterborne
OL,7,Fdisease that causes unpleasant
OL,8,Fsymptoms such as vomiting and
OL,9,Fdiarrhoea.
OL,11,FIt has led to two people being taken
OL,12,Fto hospital while hundreds of others
OL,13,Fhave fallen ill as a result of the
OL,14,Foutbreak.
OL,16,FBut on 21 May, it was announced that
OL,17,Fshareholders in the water company will
OL,18,Freceive 3.8% more in their dividend
OL,19,Fpayout than last year.
