OL,3,CWater company hikes dividend payout to
OL,4,Cshareholders amid parasite outbreak
OL,6,FThe announcement of the dividend
OL,7,Fpayment has angered the local MP whose
OL,8,Fconstituents have been most affected
OL,9,Fby the issues in Brixham.
OL,11,FConservative politician Anthony
OL,12,FMangnall MP has said Pennon, SWW's
OL,13,Fparent company, should suspend the
OL,14,Fdividend payments this year, or the
OL,15,Fcompany's CEO should resign.
OL,17,F"Obviously it's hugely disappointing
OL,18,Fat a moment where the public's
OL,19,Fconfidence in South West Water is at
OL,20,Fan all-time low they've decided to go
OL,21,Fahead and pay out dividends," he said.
