OL,6,F"I have called for Pennon to suspend
OL,7,Ftheir dividend offering, which they
OL,8,Fcan do, which they are able to do.
OL,10,F"I have also suggested that if they
OL,11,Ffail to do so, the chief executive
OL,12,Fshould take the rap for this.
OL,14,F"I'm not against dividend payments in
OL,15,Fgeneral, I'm just saying that at this
OL,16,Fpoint in time, where the public have
OL,17,Fbeen so badly let down, that we really
