OL,6,FSpeaking before the calls for her to
OL,7,Fgo, group chief executive Susan Davy
OL,8,Fsaid: "Whilst the results we are
OL,9,Fannouncing today are based on our
OL,10,Fperformance for the last financial
OL,11,Fyear, we are 100% focused on returning
OL,12,Fa safe water supply to the people and
OL,13,Fbusinesses in and around Brixham.
OL,15,F"Normal service has returned for 85%
OL,16,Fof customers but we won't stop until
OL,17,Fthe local drinking water is returned
OL,18,Fto the quality all our customers
